defaultL
defaulteonard Cheshire Disability's International Department works through five regional 
defaultoffices in Africa and Asia. We support
default children with disabilities to 
defaultget an education
default, adults with disabilities to earn a living, and all disabled people to access the rehabilitation, health and other support they need. 
defaultWe also campaign
default to put disability at the heart of international development, and support young disabled peop
defaultle to campai
defaultgn for their rights through our Young Voices p
defaultrogramme
default.
